lessons.content:
# Functions in Reaper

Functions allow you to reuse code. Here's the syntax:

```reaper
function name(param_type param_name): return_type {
    // code here
    return value;
}
```

lessons.code_example:
function greet(crypt name): void {
    harvest("Hello, " + name);
}

greet("Reaper");
